2 / 6

3 / 6
Feedback :
Number of favourable outcomes = 3 (the die throws 2, 4, 6). Total number of outcomes = 6 ( the die could throw 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 or 6). Probability = Number of favourable outcomes / Total number of outcomes = 3 / 6
Correct

